{"type":null,"faqId":33091,"title":"EPG（电子节目单）","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.29166666in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>EPG功能可以理解为电视报，即通过网络来获取广电总局的电视节目单。集节目显示、频道显示为一体，为用户提供丰富的电视节目十大功能（卖点）：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1、支持节目直接遥控，遥控你想看的节目；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、支持频道直接遥控，遥控你想看的频道；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、支持节目预约提醒，到时提醒用户观看；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4、支持频道收藏，收藏用户喜爱的频道；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>5、支持节目分类，为用户提供丰富的节目归类，包括：娱乐、体育、新闻、影视等等；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>6、支持节目推荐，根据用户喜好，主动push给用户相关节目推荐；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>7、支持3天内的节目单查看，预约；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>8、支持央视、地方频道分类显示；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>9、支持节目搜索，快速找到你喜欢的节目；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>10、支持节目信息和内容介绍，给你展示节目简介、演员、导演、主持人等；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=103524\" style=\"width:2.2458334in;height:3.2180555in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=103525\" style=\"width:2.2395833in;height:3.20625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>节目分类和频道分类</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=103526\" style=\"width:2.2826388in;height:3.2930555in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=103527\" style=\"width:2.2826388in;height:3.2902777in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>节目单和节目详情</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=103528\" style=\"width:2.2826388in;height:3.2798612in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=103529\" style=\"width:2.2819445in;height:3.25in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>影视和地方频道</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7793","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748499000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":6,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"EPG,电子节目单","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}